---
title: Honey Mustard Chicken with green beans and potato wedges
description: Some things just go together, and honey and mustard are two flavours that are most definitely meant to be. Paired with crunchy green beans and crispy potato wedges this dish is a real treat for the tastebuds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W11_IE_IEXFC0098-6_Main_high-70447d5c.jpg
